ntek\u015bcie sprzeda\u017cy i mar\u017cy.<\/li>\n<li><b>Podejmowanie decyzji<\/b>: Maj\u0105c dok\u0142adne dane o kosztach, podejmuj \u015bwiadome decyzje dotycz\u0105ce dalszego prowadzenia reklam, dostosowywania cen czy wycofania niekt\u00f3rych produkt\u00f3w.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<h2>Podsumowanie<\/h2>\n<p>Dok\u0142adne wprowadzenie koszt\u00f3w do systemu Amazon jest kluczem do oceny rentowno\u015bci Twojego biznesu. Dzi\u0119ki tym krokom mo\u017cesz lepiej zrozumie\u0107, kt\u00f3re produkty przynosz\u0105 zysk, a kt\u00f3re wymagaj\u0105 zmian w strategii.<\/p>\n<p><b>Masz wi\u0119cej pyta\u0144? Skontaktuj si\u0119 z nami.<\/b><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<h1>Jak obliczy\u0107 zyski na Amazonie: Praktyczny przewodnik<\/h1>\n<p>Czy kiedykolwiek zastanawia\u0142e\u015b si\u0119, <\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":7126,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[1],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-7125","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-ecommerce"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7125"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=7125"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/7125\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/7126"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=7125"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/eubrand.local\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\